# Vite reads VITE_* prefixed vars at build time. Copy to `.env` and adjust.

# Default `/api` lets the dev-server proxy forward calls to the local FastAPI
# backend (see `vite.config.ts`). In production, set this to your deployed
# backend origin, e.g. `https://mini-ai-api.example.com` (no trailing slash).
VITE_API_BASE=/api